 many conversations on human nature with Dors than any equation, he quickly imagined their expert blandishments, warm skin, dulcet voices, masking primordial ammonia ice. Dors had frequently made wry observations of that human sex after which she was mode
led, and she had seldom been wrong.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
