\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 The Commissioner to the immediate right of Chen called the advocate to the bench. His whisper pierced the chamber, though Hari could not hear what was said.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 When the advocate returned, he seemed a little chastened.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "We are not here to listen to speeches, Dr}{\fs20 .}{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033  Seldon. Let us assume that you have made your point. Let's focus this inquiry a little more, Professor Seldon. "}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Fine. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Let me suggest to you that your predictions of disaster might be intended to destroy public confidence in the Imperial Government for purposes of your own. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
