ly. " He waved his hand over the audience. "This courtroom may explode in the next few hours, or it may not. " Boon made a mildly disapproving face. "If it did, the future would undoubtedly be changed in some minor respects. " Hari smiled at the advocate,
 then at Linge Chen, who was not watching him. Boon's frown deepened.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
