te seemed to find this a revelation. "Ah! In that case, Dr. Seldon, we are left with this deduction to be made from your statements. You have gathered one hundred thousand people within the confines of your Project. These are insufficient to change the hi
story of Trantor within five hundred years. In other words, they cannot prevent the destruction of Trantor no matter what they do. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
