\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 The advocate stepped back, fastened a benevolent gaze on Hari, then said, slowly and with smug satisfaction, "In that case, Dr. Seldon\emdash now at
tend, sir, most carefully, for we want a considered answer. " He suddenly thrust out a well-manicured finger and shrilled: "What is the purpose of your hundred thousand?"}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
