\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Boon nodded solemnly. "Indeed, " he said.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
