\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Shall we then proceed with the trial to its final phase, or recess and continue the proceedings at a later date?"}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Hari sat up with a grunt. Boon laid a hand on his arm.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Linge Chen looked up at the ceiling. "Recess, " he murmured, and looked down again.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "We shall recess until such time as the judges believe it is expedient to resume, " the advocate said.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Hari seemed to feel himself deflating. He shook his head and glared at the Chief Commissioner, but Chen was contemplating some higher sphere of being, with a satisfaction that Hari found doubly infuriating.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 In the hallway to his chambers, Hari shouted at Boon. '"They will never be done with me! They have no decency!"}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Boon simply lifted his hands, helpless, and the guards returned Hari to his cell.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
