\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Linge Chen allowed Kreen to remove his
 judge's robes. The servant undressed his master silently and swiftly, hardly disturbing the Chief Commissioner's concentration. Chen stared blankly at the opposite wall as Kreen undid his long golden waist bands. Finally, dressed in a pale gray cassock, 
