ale humaniform raised a mediating hand. His appearance was that of a young artist, a member of the mer-ijtocrat class known as the Eccentrics, dressed in bright stripes. "Please be circumspect, Turringen. Twenty millennia have proved the futility of viole
nce among our kind. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
