nts in the dark. My name is Zorma. And yes, we here represent some ancient factions, leftover from the distant past, when deep schisms tore apart the unity of robots... a time when our struggles raged across the stars, mostly hidden from human eyes. "}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
