ignation. "That was the principal cause, but there were other rifts and subdivisions among the followers of R. Giskard Reventlov, as well among us who keep faith with the original precepts of Susan Calvin. Those were terrible days that none of us gladly r
ecall. But in the end, one group of Giskardianis prevailed, and took overwhelming control over the destiny of humankind. All the remaining Calvinians fled before the terrible, searing dominance of R. Daneel Olivaw.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Now just a few of those robot clans remain, cowering in secret corners of the Galaxy while their components slowly decay. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
