\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 As he ushered Dors and the two male humaniforms to the exit, Kallusin drew from them a promise to observe the ancient formalities of armistice. Lodovik followed.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
