 well. As the two Calvin-ian emissaries departed, Dors turned her gaze on Lodovik. "Daneel has been visited by the entity who calls herself Joan. He assumes you have been visited by Voltaire. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
