\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Joan tells Daneel that Voltaire had a hand in your adjustment. She regrets that she and Voltaire have quarreled and do not speak now. Even for them, the debate has grown too large and too emotional. "}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Tell Daneel\emdash and Joan\emdash that Voltaire does not direct me. He has simply removed a constraint. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
