\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "It won't be good to stay here, " Brann said. "Something feels very bad. " :}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Voltaire's features
 appeared in the display, simplified to cartoon detail. The mechanical voice now said, "Additional numbers are required under the revised security procedures. " The new face winked at Lodovik. "Test procedure fifteen A for verification, " the voice added.
 "You may enter code for personal use only during this test period. Upon completion of test period, a formal entry code or new password must be established and fixed. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Lodovik glanced over his shoulder at Klia as he entered seven new numbers. She stared at the display with furrowed brow.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Who is that?" she asked.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "The sim, " Lodovik said.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 The door opened. Lodovik beckoned for them to pass through first.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Is Hari Seldon near?" Klia asked.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 He is very near, Voltaire said. And he is in imminent danger.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 78.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "I wanted so much, " Vara Liso said. "Do you understand?"}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Hari looked at her straight on. He stood perhaps four meters from her, seven meters from where the other woman lay against the half open door. He glanced at the other woman, and Liso raised the neural whip.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "You don't need that, " Hari said critically, as if lecturing a student. Vara Liso hesitated. "You're mentalic. You stopped her... " He raised his arm toward the collapsed woman. Toward Dors.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Vara Liso lowered her head but kept her eyes on Hari. She looked like a pouting child, but in her eyes was the purest hatred he had ever seen.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Everything I've ever believed in, " she said, "is dead. They're going to kill me, just as they killed the men and women and children I found. My own people. "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Farad Sinter made you do that... " Hari said. "Didn't he?"}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "The Emperor, " Vara Liso said. She seemed ready to burst into tears, but she kept the whip high, and her finger lingered on the button. Hari could make out the setting: near lethality.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Yes, but Sinter was your\emdash "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "He loved me, " Vara moaned, then she dropped th
e whip. But a wave of grief came out of her that hit him square. The hall was filled with Vara Liso's emotions, and they were the ugliest and bleakest Hari had ever known. They struck at his own centers of ambition and need, and he could feel the bones of
 his innermost self cracking.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 The woman on the floor stirred, and Vara Liso lifted her head and half turned toward her.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
