e would be blinded, she was sure. Vara Liso could not broadcast with such intensity for so long, and indeed the undirected flood was narrowing, finding a channel. It was concentrating, and even though it suddenly diminished by half, what Vara Liso was thr
owing directly at Klia doubled in strength.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
