\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Lodovik stepped toward the woman, now twisted and gnarled like an ancient willow.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Klia lifted her head, opened her eyes, prepared to be blinded, and saw down a short brilliant funnel of hatred to the eyes, all that were left of Vara Liso\emdash a pair of desperate and hate-filled eyes.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Brann will die, too.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
