Never had she used her abilities to harm. Even making Lodovik dance had injured her sense of propriety and justice; she had never really believed she could do anything to Hari Seldon. She would think of her father, whom she had once made wet h
is pants... and the effort would collapse.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
