 not stop. This was what humans had done to each other throughout their history, and it hurt him that he had such freedom as well: freedom to harm and to kill. But he was under no misapprehension that he was no better than this gnarled and hideous female.
 Quite clearly she was evil; she was antihuman.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
