\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 "Once he was known as Demerzel, " Linge Chen said.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Prothon drew his head back and narrowed his eyes dubiously, but did not contradict the Chief Commissioner.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
