 " Chen, for the first time that day, smiled up at Prothon. That smile was peculiar, almost wolfish, and Chen's eyes glittered with mixed emotions. "I suspect he has been directing my efforts in various ways for years now, always to my advantage... " He s
aid again, musing softly, "Always to my advantage... "}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
