opposite humans. " Joan stretched until she filled their still-limited thought-space, voluptuously enjoying her fresh reintegration. "It is holy to be One, " she said. "With me?"}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 For a time, Joan did not reply. Then, with something like a sigh, she accepted his closeness. The two wove an old world around them, like a cocoon, to while away the long centuries until there would be answers.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 From a maintenance tower overlooking Streeling and the oceans of Sleep, Dream, and Peace, still open and glowing with an e
xuberance of decaying algae, Daneel watched the ship captained by Mors Planch rise above the domed surface of Trantor until it vanished in the thick layer of clouds.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Soon, he would go to Eos as well, though not byway of Kal-gan. But he wanted to return for Hari, at the end. Daneel, if such was possible, had always felt a special regard for Hari.}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Dancers face formed an expression of puzzlement and sadness, without his directly willing the change. The expression came unbidden, and with a start, he realized it
. Perhaps what he had said to Lodovik now applied to him. If, after twenty thousand years, he was to become human...}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 He smoothed those features, that expression, returning his face to calm alertness.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 I will never be quite done with humans, he told himself. But I must stand back\emdash for the time being\emdash and resist my drive to render assistance\emdash 
this much Lodovik has taught me. They have exceeded my capacity\emdash so many hundreds of billions! Keeping the Chaos Worlds in check has only kept humanity safe until now. I must study and learn. It is clear that humanity will}{
\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 soon undergo another transformation... The strong mentalics point to a kind of birth.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Perhaps I can help ease that birth. Then I will be done at last. 
Daneel could not ignore the contradictions; nor could he escape them. Dors had her mission, the job that defined her, and he had always had his mission.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Only one thing was certain.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
\par }{\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 Never again would he play the roles he had once played. Demerzel and all those who had gone before were dead.}{\f1\fs20\lang1033\langfe1033\langnp1033 
